Package: saasr
Type: Package
Title: Simulate subscription business models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Christopher", "Peters", , "chris.peters@zapier.com", role = c("aut", "cre")
    ))
Maintainer: Christopher Peters <chris.peters@zapier.com>
Description: Subscriptions are a great way to finance the development of software,
    but relatively little has been written about their statistical properties.
    This package attempts to provide tools to make analysis and simulation of
    subscription billing models easy.
